DELAY_TO_GLIDE_SIZE(delay)
	Value: (round((clamp(((32 / max(delay / world.tick_lag, 1)) * (1 - (SStime_track.time_dilation_current / 100)) * (CONFIG_GET(number/glide_size_mod) * 0.01)), MIN_GLIDE_SIZE, MAX_GLIDE_SIZE)), 0.1))
	Comment: 
	Defined in: code\__DEFINES\movement.dm : 7
	Number of references: 0

	Comment:
